  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/6e12376057453d3ba92c49b1536f6756.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Skotos is an intense first-person platformer that explores the fear of darkness. Players will journey through ominous environments while solving platforming puzzles, exploring unknown territory, and facing their greatest fears.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/9f14a9b4435f0b2dfb05934ceef6a8a9.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics-Based Lantern</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.poster.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.webm?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.mp4?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Trapped in complete Darkness, use your physics based lantern to light your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Psychological Platforming</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/275e0db6bc6f6cbd48a303f0a09f25d7.poster.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/275e0db6bc6f6cbd48a303f0a09f25d7.webm?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/275e0db6bc6f6cbd48a303f0a09f25d7.mp4?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Brave the darkness with your trusty lantern as you platform in complete darkness.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Horrors Of The Darkness</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/a75613197dddf9ef9ca4d48f67872deb.poster.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/a75613197dddf9ef9ca4d48f67872deb.webm?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/a75613197dddf9ef9ca4d48f67872deb.mp4?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The darkness can manifest itself in many forms.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/6e12376057453d3ba92c49b1536f6756.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=120 /></span><br><br>Skotos is an intense first-person platformer that explores the fear of darkness. Players will journey through ominous environments while solving platforming puzzles, exploring unknown territory, and facing their greatest fears.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/9f14a9b4435f0b2dfb05934ceef6a8a9.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics-Based Lantern</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.poster.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.webm?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/8e36041084520753ca6348168d9e5fb1.mp4?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Trapped in complete Darkness, use your physics based lantern to light your way.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Psychological Platforming</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/275e0db6bc6f6cbd48a303f0a09f25d7.poster.avif?t=1682972106\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1721830/extras/275e0db6bc6f6cbd48a303f0a09f25d7.webm?t=1682972106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"h